ppälä, A., Shangguan, M., Sinnhuber, M., Tourpali, K., Usoskin, I., van de Kamp, M., Verronen, P. T., and Versick, S.: Solar forcing for CMIP6 (v3.2), Geosci. Model Dev., 10, 2247–2302, <a href="https://doi.org/10.5194/gmd-10-2247-2017">https://doi.org/10.5194/gmd-10-2247-2017</a>, 2017. <a href="https://gmd.copernicus.org/articles/13/2149/2020/#xref_paren.24" class="scrollto" data-fixed-element=".auto-fixed-top-forced.article-title">a</a></span></p><p class="ref" id="bib1.bibx19"><span class="mixed-citation">Mattoso, M., Werner, C., Travassos, G. H., Braganholo, V., Ogasawara, E.,
